      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/apparel-retailer-express-files-us-bankruptcy-protection-close-over-100-stores-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[时尚零售商 Express Inc 周一表示，已根据美国破产法第 11 章申请破产，并打算关闭 100 多家商店。]]></description>
